{"tid":1124631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【共軍車禍】大圍貨車收掣不及撞軍車　無人受傷","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T08:44:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a67890bfc0912a59ebf6372b512dd97817886612","tid":1124631,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:57:03.000Z","msg":"今（24日）上午8時35分，一輛解放軍駐港部隊車輛沿尖山隧道往沙田方向行駛，途徑大圍附近時，因前方汽車切線而放緩行駛，尾隨的貨車收掣不及撞向軍車。意外中無人受傷，貨車車頭輕微受損、解放軍車車尾部份凹陷。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n貨車司機表示，貨車從尖山隧道駛出，欲前往沙田送貨，惟前面解放軍車突然收慢，並打算切線往大圍方向，他得悉對方準備切線已放緩行車，怎料對方突然停下，貨車收掣不及撞向軍車尾部，「睇住佢cut、佢突然間停都冇辦法」。<br />\n <br />\n「ZG」車牌為解放軍駐港部隊車輛<br />\n<br />\n根據駐軍法規定，軍車屬國家特種車輛，倘執勤時遇車禍或事故，可獲豁免配合執法，警察無權查處，要等軍隊督查員到場，因為軍車的任何行動都可能涉及軍事機密。而解放軍駐港部隊車輛的車牌大多是「ZG」字頭，「ZG」為普通話拼音ZhuGang（駐港）的簡稱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2714271/org/94745744f7ba520e3357e10f7e61c8f5.jpg/qId9JFSfrYP5y9GsRSK0MHm2MkMkZOJ6lGtau5RrWrs?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2714271%2Forg%2F94745744f7ba520e3357e10f7e61c8f5.jpg%2FqId9JFSfrYP5y9GsRSK0MHm2MkMkZOJ6lGtau5RrWrs%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=6f908d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/321284/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E6%94%B6%E6%8E%A3%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8D%E8%BB%8A-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F321284%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%258E%25A3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=444f7976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/321284/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E6%94%B6%E6%8E%A3%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8D%E8%BB%8A-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"690eabbd6ad94c8483ba30cd78602432e2939766","tid":1124631,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"分明前車魯莽駕駛啦"},{"pid":"147a6bc285d3df81e242143439f40a1c35777995","tid":1124631,"uid":18955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"軍車屬國家特種車輛，倘執勤時遇車禍或事故，可獲豁免配合執法，警察無權查處，要等軍隊督查員到場，因為軍車的任何行動都可能涉及軍事機密。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n不過中午渣部軍車去入油<br />\n<br />\n順路買個唐餐外賣<br />\n<br />\n又唔係咩國家機密嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小小公器私用咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f307b6a6cbf99fb5ed05f4d8b423b157024cce4b","tid":1124631,"uid":55914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:24:41.000Z","msg":"「睇住佢cut、佢突然間停都冇辦法」貨車佬RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d159d07a52e011d7e1d3ac8aec95de59f7eee7","tid":1124631,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"點解唔抵制日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解放軍正漢奸"},{"pid":"487d623546961d7fc34ce6c49e4f2a340ef5a1d4","tid":1124631,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"可能又係強國式搵路<br />\n就係起公路分叉位前急停<br />\n<br />\n累已累人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8355796558f165050235d45c7e1f755d379728","tid":1124631,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"貨車司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5c4a0af611156bbe208ee28454c6be5153740f","tid":1124631,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"督戰隊？"}]}